# State Specs

## Purpose

This directory contains generated bookkeeping state contracts when the loop needs durable runtime state.

## Contents

- `state-overview.md`: generated state authority, boundary, entity, transition, and invariant overview when emitted.
- `schema.sql`: generated sqlite schema when sqlite is selected.
- `seed.toml`: generated initial state facts when deterministic initialization is needed.
- `invariants.toml`: generated invariant names and validation expectations when emitted.
- `records/`: generated JSONL record schemas when JSONL is selected.
